snippet.title: The Christmas Noose Song
snippet.description:
Download the song: https://rustycage.bandcamp.com/track/the-christmas-noose-song
It will be up on spotify and itunes too late.  Most likely a week after christmas lol

My comic book ► https://rustycage.tv/shop
apparel ► https://teespring.com/stores/rusty-cage
TikTok ► @OfficialRustyCage
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/Rstycg
Instagram ► https://instagram.com/thegangstalker
Patreon ► https://www.patreon.com/RustyCage
MUSIC ► https://rustycage.bandcamp.com/

LYRICS:

All I want for Christmas is a length of rope to tie into a noose
So I can hang up everything I need to hang, it's good for every use
I could hang a reef, I could hang a candy cane, I could hang some mistletoe,
I could even hang a nose by the fire place with a holly jolly glow

Hang yourself a little ornament upon the christmas tree
Don't you wish you dedicated as Santa seems to be
End your life of sorrow, cause nows the time for cheer
And I hope that when I look under the Christmas tree
there'll be a noose for me this year

Now I know the noose has a real dark past that many folks abhor
but I think the time has come for us to change all that
and make it fun once more
After all, it's just a rope with a useless knot
like the one on Santa's sleigh
So, lets all hang around the Christmas tree and have ourselves a happy holiday

Hang yourself a little ornament upon the christmas tree
Don't you wish you dedicated as Santa seems to be
End your life of sorrow, cause nows the time for cheer
And I hope that when I look under the Christmas tree
there'll be a noose for me this year
